     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <l>THis little Booke for priuate vse,</l>
   <l>was pen'd some time agoe;</l>
   <l>And now diuulg'd for priuate freinds,</l>
   <l>His Author wills it soe,</l>
   <l>But if it come to others handes,</l>
   <l>And they some profit gaine:</l>
   <l>Then thanke his friends, that for their sakes,</l>
   <l>He hath tooke all this paine.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>ROGER KNIGHT.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
